### =============================================
### BOOKS
### =============================================

### Obtener todos los libros
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### Obtener un libro por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/books/

### Crear un nuevo libro
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Clean Code",
    "description": "A handbook of agile software craftsmanship",
    "author": "Robert C. Martin",
    "pages": 464,
    "genre": "Programming",
    "publishedDate": "2008-08-01",
    "lenguage": "Inglés"
}

### Actualizar un libro
PUT http://localhost:3000/books/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Clean Code Updated",
    "description": "Updated version",
    "author": "Robert C. Martin",
    "pages": 500,
    "genre": "Software Engineering",
    "publishedDate": "2008-08-01",
    "lenguage": "Inglés"
}

### Eliminar un libro
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/

### =============================================
### AUTHORS
### =============================================

### Obtener todos los autores
GET http://localhost:3000/authors

### Obtener un autor por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/authors/69beff1b411800232778ff8b
### Crear un nuevo autor
POST http://localhost:3000/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Robert",
    "lastName": "Martin",
    "nationality": "Estadounidense",
    "birthDate": "1952-12-05",
    "bio": "Ingeniero de software, autor y conferencista conocido como Uncle Bob.",
    "genre": "Tecnología",
    "activeYears": 40,
    "website": "https://cleancoder.com"
}

### Actualizar un autor
PUT http://localhost:3000/authors/69befee8411800232778ff84
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Robert",
    "lastName": "C. Martin",
    "nationality": "Estadounidense",
    "birthDate": "1952-12-05",
    "bio": "Ingeniero de software y autor de Clean Code y The Clean Coder.",
    "genre": "Tecnología",
    "activeYears": 45,
    "website": "https://cleancoder.com"
}

### Eliminar un autor
DELETE http://localhost:3000/authors/69befee8411800232778ff84
